    <h2>My Work</h2>

    <article class="project-container code-editor">
      <div class="title">
      <h3>Code Editor</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>WinForms</li>
          <li>C#</li>
          <li>.NET 4.8</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <p>A light-weight code editor built with WinForms and Visual Studio. Open folders, modify and save files and edit multiple documents concurrently.
