    </article>

    <img id="code-editor"
       src="/images/projects/codeeditor.jpg"
       alt="WinForms based Code Editor" />

    <article class="project-container unity-game">
       <div class="title">
          <ul>
             <li>Unity Engine</li>
             <li>C#</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Video Game</h3>
       </div>
       <p>
        A finished game experience. Inifnite procedural generation, chunk management, occlusion culling, 2D newtonian physics, 17 different types of stars, dozens of upgrades.
        Players can see how high of a score they can get and play in browser or download for multiple platforms.
       </p>
    </article>

    <img
      id="video-game"
      src="/images/projects/videogame.jpg"
      alt="WinForms based Code Editor"/>
